      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Last week I stayed at The Azure Resort, and while it had some downsides such as slow service, the staff were definitely as nice as they come. The breakfast could probably be cheaper, but man, did I love the breakfast. The rooms weren't the most spacious, but we had a great view of the ocean, which made up for it. The pool area was simply fantastic with great amenities. Even the breakfast drinks were excellent. The resort definitely has a need for some upgrades, and I would love to see more attention on improving the rooms and service speed. But, it definitely gave me more nature and relaxation time, and the pool area made it a tough decision to choose a new place to visit. I think it’s been worth the time, even though it could be improved further for future visits. If you love ocean views, this resort is a must-see!",
